# integration/

BATS integration test suite for Intent. Tests core functionality, project workflows, and end-to-end scenarios including project initialization, steel thread creation, and error handling.

## Files

- `core_functionality.bats` -- Essential functionality tests: help, project detection, backup naming, silent failure prevention
- `end_to_end.bats` -- Workflow integration tests: project creation, steel thread management, error handling across commands
